## ğŸ§­ About the Project

A full-stack **Tourist Management System** built with Java EE (JSP/Servlet) and MySQL. This web application allows tourists to register and log in to explore travel services, while administrators can manage the entire platform from a dedicated admin panel.

> Built as a part of academic/personal project demonstrating full-stack Java web development with MVC architecture.

---

## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ‘¤ User Side
- âœ… **User Registration** â€” Secure sign-up with form validation
- âœ… **User Login / Logout** â€” Session-based authentication
- âœ… **View Tourist Packages** â€” Browse available destinations
- âœ… **Responsive UI** â€” HTML/CSS based clean interface

### ğŸ” Admin Panel
- âœ… **Admin Login** â€” Separate secure admin access
- âœ… **Manage Users** â€” View and manage registered users
- âœ… **Manage Packages** â€” Add, update, delete tourist packages
- âœ… **Dashboard Overview** â€” See system stats at a glance

### ğŸ—„ï¸ Database
- âœ… **MySQL Backend** â€” Persistent data storage
- âœ… **Relational Schema** â€” Users, packages, bookings tables
- âœ… **JDBC Connectivity** â€” Java to MySQL via JDBC driver

